{"tid":110974,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得有咩食物應該禁止食用？","createTime":"2017-02-07T05:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T06:40:14.000Z","uid":78533,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"973821cc0f95b864b3846a6e40eee1e72136d03c","tid":110974,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"個人認為好多食物如同生物兵器！<br />\n而我覺得最危險既係水產！！！<br />\n<br />\n我稱為第一類危險<br />\n<br />\n貝類-殺傷力極高<br />\n攻擊方法：大多產於淺水區，經常以利刃割傷身旁人類！<br />\n<br />\n魚類-植入式兵器<br />\n攻擊方法：以白滑鮮甜魚肉吸引人類，以暗藏殺戈魚骨直接插入口中！<br />\n<br />\n甲殼類-魔鬼的咀咒<br />\n攻擊方法：以鮮甜肉厚等美味迷惑人類，再以尖峰利刃的甲殼攻擊企圖進食時的人類！<br />\n<br />\n種族特質：毒、致敏感、食用可口"},{"pid":"b9a95bef5e4d15cc32067c1519847fa26a5b7c2b","tid":110974,"uid":79145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7338b6ce5e5f4353f8d8c2d6dedb94db366cab9","tid":110974,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:01:26.000Z","msg":"負評"},{"pid":"bc2d3d6dce39e84420c799e42ae568747be1925d","tid":110974,"uid":62722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:02:56.000Z","msg":"樓主傻左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e5ee5f84891a14e130b4012737d0609b8f1951","tid":110974,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:04:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4f29e928fb6ef44b55190ad980446812d9a36e5","tid":110974,"uid":83092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負評</blockquote><br />\n已負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f602765acafc8401823dd600e6be9db7fdc8bf34","tid":110974,"uid":2440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:05:31.000Z","msg":"中二病發作？"},{"pid":"52ad56a1c187072f1b017902d517eca42171adcc","tid":110974,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco